{"title_page": "Bezd\u011bkov (Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District)", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Bezd\u011bkov\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=Bezd\u011bkov(HB)-n\u00e1ves-2.JPG\n|image_shield=Bezd\u011bkov (okres Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod) znak.jpg\n|image_flag=Bezd\u011bkov (okres Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod) vlajka.jpg\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[Vyso\u010dina Region|Vyso\u010dina]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District|Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod]]\n|coordinates = {{coord|49|43|45|N|15|43|42|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n|pushpin_map=Czech Republic|area_total_km2=5.35\n|population_total=242|population_as_of=2006\n|population_density_km2=auto\n|elevation_m=433\n|postal_code_type=Postal&nbsp;code|postal_code=583&nbsp;01\n|website=http://bezdekov.sweb.cz/\n}}\n\n'''Bezd\u011bkov''' ({{IPA-cs|\u02c8b\u025bz\u025f\u025bkof}}) is a village and municipality (''[[obec]]'') in [[Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District]] in the [[Vyso\u010dina Region]] of the Czech Republic.\n\nThe municipality covers an area of {{convert|5.35|km2|sqmi}}, and has a population of 242 (as at 3&nbsp;July 2006).\n\nBezd\u011bkov lies approximately {{convert|18|km|mi|0}} north-east of [[Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod]], {{convert|39|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} north of [[Jihlava]], and {{convert|102|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} south-east of [[Prague]].\n\n==References==\n*[http://www.czso.cz/lexikon/mos_vdb.nsf/okresy/CZ0631/ Czech Statistical Office: Municipalities of Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District]{{dead link|date=July 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}\n\n{{commons category|Bezd\u011bkov (Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District)}}\n{{Havl\u00ed\u010dk\u016fv Brod District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bezdekov}}\n[[Category:Villages in