{"title_page": "Bezd\u011bdovice", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Bezd\u011bdovice\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=|image_shield=|image_flag=\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[South Bohemian Region|South Bohemian]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[Strakonice District|Strakonice]]\n|coordinates = {{coord|49|27|4|N|13|52|44|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n|pushpin_map=Czech Republic|area_total_km2=5.82\n|population_total=312|population_as_of=\n|population_density_km2=auto\n|elevation_m=448\n|postal_code_type=Postal&nbsp;code|postal_code=388&nbsp;01\n|website=http://www.municipal.cz/bezdedovice/\n}}\n\n'''Bezd\u011bdovice''' is a village and municipality (''[[obec]]'') in [[Strakonice District]] in the [[South Bohemian Region]] of the Czech Republic.\n\nThe municipality covers an area of {{convert|5.82|km2|sqmi}}, and has a population of 312.\n\nBezd\u011bdovice lies approximately {{convert|22|km|mi|0}} north of [[Strakonice]], {{convert|69|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} north-west of [[\u010cesk\u00e9 Bud\u011bjovice]], and {{convert|81|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} south-west of [[Prague]].\n\n==References==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20080523194605/http://www.czso.cz/lexikon/mos_vdb.nsf/okresy/CZ0316 Czech Statistical Office: Municipalities of Strakonice District]\n\n{{commons category|Bezd\u011bdovice}}\n{{Strakonice District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bezdedovice}}\n[[Category:Villages in Strakonice District]]\n\n\n{{SouthBohemia-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Bezd\u011bdovice\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=|image_shield=|image_flag=\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[South Bohemian Region|South Bohemian]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of th